k, Beşiktaş r7 - Şub 2013.JPG|frameless|125x125px]] |[[Istanbul|İstanbul]] |1913 |commissioned by [[Grand Vizier]] [[Nevşehirli Damat Ibrahim Pasha]] (1666–1730). |- |[[Mosque with the Spiral Minaret|Burmalı Mescit Mosque]] |[[File:Burmalı Mescit Camii.jpg|frameless|165x165px]] |[[Istanbul|İstanbul]] |1550 |Ottoman mosque |- |[[Defterdar Mosque]] |[[File:Defterdar Mosque.jpg|frameless|125x125px]] |[[Istanbul|İstanbul]] |1542 |Ottoman mosque, commissioned by [[Defterdar]] Nazlı Mahmut Efendi. |- |[[Dolmabahçe Mosque]] |[[File:Istanbul Bosphorus Dolmabahce Mosque IMG 7575 1800.jpg|frameless|125x125px]] |İstanbul |1855 |Ottoman mosque, commissioned by queen mother Bezmi Alem Valide Sultan |}
