According to [[Ayyavazhi mythology]] the situation of the whole Universe changes as the [[Kaliyan]] was born, and '''Thiru Nadana Ula''' is the part which was told by [[Shiva|Sivan]] in [[Akilam eight]] about the universal changes. It consist of 21 [[Vennpa]]s.

